# Day 30 – Supply Chain Builder using Claude AI

## 🎯 Objective

The objective of this task was to build an interactive Supply Chain Builder using Claude AI. The application helps users understand the fundamentals of supply chain management by allowing them to design and optimize a supply chain while observing how each decision affects business performance.

---

## 📦 Project Overview

Supply Chain Builder is an educational React-based web application that teaches supply chain concepts through an interactive simulation. Users build a supply chain by selecting suppliers, factory locations, warehouse strategies, transportation methods, and inventory levels while monitoring live business metrics.

---

## ✨ Features Implemented

### 🏢 Company Generation

- Random Company Profile
- Industry & Product Information
- Countries Served
- Demand Level

---

### 🚚 Supply Chain Design

- Supplier Strategy Selection
- Factory Location Selection
- Warehouse Strategy
- Transportation Method
- Inventory Strategy

---

### 📊 Live Business Metrics

- Cost
- Delivery Speed
- Risk
- Customer Satisfaction
- Sustainability

---

### 📈 Final Optimization Dashboard

- Overall Supply Chain Score
- Strengths
- Weaknesses
- Biggest Risk
- Recommended Improvements
- Replay Simulation

